### Seed doctors and tests
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/seed

### List all doctors
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/doctors

### List all tests
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/tests

### Create a patient
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/patient/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
"name": "John Doe",
"phone": "+91-9876543210",
"address": "123 Main Street, City"
}

### Get patient by phone
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/patient/phone/+91-9876543210

### Book a test
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/booking/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
"patient_name": "John Doe",
"patient_phone": "+91-9876543210",
"test_name": "CBC Test",
"collection_address": "123 Main Street, City"
}

### Get booking by ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/booking/BOOKING_ID_HERE

### List bookings by phone
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/bookings/+91-9876543210

### Upload a report (admin/lab use)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/report/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
"booking_id": "BOOKING_ID_HERE",
"results": "Hemoglobin: 14.5 g/dL\nWBC: 7,200 /uL\nRBC: 5.0 M/uL\nPlatelets: 250,000 /uL\n\nAll values are within normal range."
}

### Download report by booking ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/report/BOOKING_ID_HERE
